      "content": "i know there's help but it's just... it's not about the money anymore. it's the math of it all. i look at the numbers and i see how much of their lives i'm consuming just to stay afloat. if i wasn't here, none of this extra pressure would exist. they could actually breathe. it feels like my existence is just a subtraction from their happiness.",
